      "content": "it feels like the only logical thing left. everything is just so loud and heavy and i'm so fundamentally drained. everyone expects me to find a \"way forward\" or \"bounce back,\" but what if there isn't a way forward? what if this is just how it ends? it feels like the noise only stops if everything just... ceases.",
